'''''Arbeiter-Zeitung''''' ('Workers Newspaper') was a newspaper in [[Luxembourg]], the central organ of the [[Workers Party of Luxembourg]] 1924&ndash;1927. In 1927 another newspaper, ''[[Tageblatt|Escher Tageblatt]]'', became the main party organ.<ref name="kow">Kowalski, Werner. ''[https://books.google.com/books?id=83QdPwAACAAJ Geschichte der sozialistischen arbeiter-internationale: 1923 - 19]''. Berlin: Dt. Verl. d. Wissenschaften, 1985. p. 308</ref>
