'''Ona de Sants-Montjuïc''' is a local radio station in [[Barcelona]] city, broadcasting at 94.6 FM. They also transmit their programs through their website on the [[internet]].

Ona Popular de Sants (the first name of this station) was inaugurated in 1985 at the Ateneu Popular de Sants, as an activity of this cultural association.

Ona de Sants-Montjuïc is a local and cultural radio station, approved by the Catalan government.

